      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;timestamp-wrapper&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;timestamp&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;2020-05-03 Sun 18:02&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-elisp&#34; data-lang=&#34;elisp&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;;; emsenn&amp;#39;s land management elisp&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;;; (elme)&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;(require &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;ht&lt;/span&gt;)&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;;; data&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;(setq elme-catalog (ht-create))&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;;; functions&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;(defun elme-add-specimen! (id info)&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  (ht-set! elme-catalog id info))&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;(defun elme-get-specimen (id)&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  (ht-get elme-catalog id))&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;(defun elme-get-specimen-attribute (id attr)&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  (ht-get (ht-get elme-catalog id) attr))&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;(defun elme-get-specimen-species (id)&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  (elme-get-specimen-attribute id &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;species&lt;/span&gt;))&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;;; examples&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;(elme-add-specimen! &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; (ht (&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;species&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;foobar&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)))&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;(elme-get-specimen &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;)&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;(elme-get-specimen-attribute &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;species&lt;/span&gt;)&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;(elme-get-specimen-species &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;)&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2020-05-04 Monday</title>
      <link>https://emsenn.net/library/ecology/domains/projects/domains/makha-sa-nursery-website-2020/domains/2020/domains/05/04/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://emsenn.net/library/ecology/domains/projects/domains/makha-sa-nursery-website-2020/domains/2020/domains/05/04/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;timestamp-wrapper&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;timestamp&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;2020-05-04 Mon 08:02&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;I&amp;rsquo;m sitting outside my front door, listening to the morning birds and A Tribe Called Red, smelling the various herbs of the garden on the wind: whiffs of curry plant and thyme.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;More quickly than expected, the nursery has developed into a legitimate project, which has motivated me to come back to looking at how to handle its data.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
